        }
      ],
      "updated": 1782554659487,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "the brain discarded 70%-80% new,\nunpracticed information within the\nfirst 24 hours.\nthats why memory need\nreinforcement = (recall + repeat).\nspaced repetition= the memory\nstrengten over time not in\npanic(cramming), so 1 hours in 3\ndays better than 3 hours in a day.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "the brain discarded 70%-80% new, unpracticed information within the first 24 hours.\nthats why memory need reinforcement = (recall + repeat).\nspaced repetition= the memory strengten over time not in panic(cramming), so 1 hours in 3 days better than 3 hours in a day.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
