      "text": "the environment secretly trains the\nmemory. if study with noise or any\ndistractions then, you will learn the\ndistraction and attention to actual\nstudy material is shallow. protect the\n30mins~ study session aggressively and\nto enter deep memory encoding.\nmemory formation requires uninterupted\ninteraction.\n",
